93 (3) A trustee in bankruptcy, executor, administrator, or receiver who has presented proof
94 of such status to the secondary metals recycler;
95 (4) Any public official acting under judicial process or authority who has presented proof
96 of such status to the secondary metals recycler;
97 (5) A sale on the execution, or by virtue, of any process issued by a court if proof thereof
